-Ginoong Liang!

00:35:29.330 --> 00:35:30.590
-Bilis!
-Multo ng Tubig.

00:35:30.830 --> 00:35:31.800
Ayos ka lang ba?

00:35:31.930 --> 00:35:32.860
Nadulas ang kamay ko,

00:35:33.290 --> 00:35:34.100
kaya may nabangga ako.

00:35:34.100 --> 00:35:34.810
Malubha ba ang iyong pinsala?

00:35:34.810 --> 00:35:36.390
Kailangan mo bang magpatingin sa doktor?

00:35:36.390 --> 00:35:37.790
Wala pong anuman, Ginoong Liang.

00:35:37.930 --> 00:35:39.290
Hindi ba't sinabi ni Master Huang

00:35:39.810 --> 00:35:40.750
na ngayon,

00:35:41.210 --> 00:35:42.610
wala ni isa sa atin ang pwedeng umalis dito?

00:35:42.710 --> 00:35:43.160
Mabilis,

00:35:43.160 --> 00:35:43.890
bumangon ka muna.

00:35:43.940 --> 00:35:44.930
Kaya ko itong tiisin.

00:35:45.560 --> 00:35:46.540
Kaya ko pa ring ipagpatuloy ang pagtatrabaho,

00:35:46.540 --> 00:35:47.100
Ginoong Liang

00:35:47.100 --> 00:35:48.100
Tingnan ko muna.

00:35:51.020 --> 00:35:52.690
Malamang nasugatan niya ang buto.

00:35:53.100 --> 00:35:53.700
Kung gayon.

00:35:54.870 --> 00:35:56.090
Magpapadala ako ng isang tao

00:35:56.270 --> 00:35:57.530
para dalhin ka sa doktor.

00:35:58.040 --> 00:35:59.170
Hindi na kailangan, Ginoong Liang.

00:35:59.430 --> 00:36:00.850
Hindi ko hahayaang ang iba

00:36:01.350 --> 00:36:03.010
lumabag sa mga patakaran dahil sa akin.

00:36:03.730 --> 00:36:04.260
